snippet.textDisplay: Jeffree I ordered my palette yesterday, with a few other items and I can’t wait to get it. I have hazel eyes and when I wear purple shadows it makes my eyes look more green. I hope on a future palette you will do ones with green/peach and coral, cause those make my eyes look more green as well. Folks really need to wait till they get the palette before they start moaning about the colors, because the colors will look much better in person. Plus the colors are telling a purple story, and as with all stories you need others characters to make the story interesting and/or fun. And I think you’ve done a lovely job. 💜💜💜
